name: Special Edition Black/Azure wool fitted flawless
description:
Here we have a new Special Edition fitted flawless.  

This limited edition cap is an all black flawless.  Button and undervisor are in a special azure blue wool fabric for a striking contrast. Undervisor is called the flip visor style.  The blue fabric is visible around rim of visor.  Crown and upper visor are in black wool.  The majority of New Era caps are now made of polyester.  We thought we'd try one in wool, just like they used to be.

Limited run on these fitteds.  

Remember, if you are a Mason, hit me up for the discount code.

name: Special Edition Woodland Camo fitted flawless
description:
Here we have a new Special Edition fitted flawless.  The crown, and visor are in the classic Woodland Camo pattern.  100% cotton.  No two caps will be the same.  Undervisor and button are in black.  All embroidery is in black for that subdued look.  Small S&C in flawless position on front.  2BE1 ASK1 on the back, and the iconic New Era flag on the side.

Limited run on these fitteds.  

Remember, if you are a Mason, hit me up for the discount code.

name: Sky Blue fitted 59Fifty
description: Here we have our latest fitted from New Era.  This model is in Sky blue with a raised 3D square and compass w/G embroidered on the front.  A white New Era flag is on the side as well as a white button.  Clean with no embroidery on the back.  A great cap in honor of our blue lodge.

name: New Dark Navy Snap-Back
description: Here we have another snap-back.  This comes in a dark navy with bold, golden yellow embroidery.  Large raised 3D square and compass w/G embroidered on the front.  New Era flag on the side, and with a matching button and adjustable snap back enclosure.  A classic colorway!

name: All Black Snap-Back
description:
Here we have and all black adjustable Snap-back.  

All black crown, visor, and under visor and button.  Features a full size square and compass w/ G embroidered on the front in black.  Black New Era flag.  Black adjustable snap back.

name: F&AM T-shirt (fitted)
description:
Now Available!!!

This is our hommage to a classic punk shirt. This is a fitted lightweight 100% cotton ringspun 7 oz.  Printing process is water based color discharge.  Which means after washing there is virtually no feeling of the print.  Nice and soft, light weight! 

Available from size M to 2XL

name: New Era 5950 Fitted Cap - Black
description:
This is New Era's original fitted cap. The 59FIFTY fitted requires 22 steps to make it perfect. Finishing touches like the taping, labeling and their symbolic New Era Flag on the left-wear side makes it the authentic, premium cap of choice. Raised embroidered logo on front, flat brim with "memento mori" skull and crossbones embroidered on the back.

Colour is black with a black visor and black button. Square & Compass in black.  This is the model I call "stealth", the cap that started it all for Grip or token.

When it comes to caps, there is no better cap then the New Era 5950 fitted cap.

Please note:  All hats are shipped with factory flat visor.  The visor can be curved or left flat depending on your preference.

name: Graphite with Black visor
description:
Graphite crown with black visor fitted 59Fifty  Features raised 3D embroidered black Square & Compass with graphite outline and a graphite NE flag on the side.  Memento Mori skull n bones on the back in black and grey.  Black underviser, sweatband, and taping.

Cap ships with flat brim from factory.  You can curve if you wish.

Remember, if you are an active Mason, please contact me and I will supply you with a discount code.

name: New Era 5950 Fitted Cap - Navy
description:
Here is my current favorite cap! 

This is a fitted New Era 5950 in Dark Navy with a retro kelly green undervisor.

Features a Square & Compass embroidered in dark charcoal with a metallic silver outline.  The New Era flag is embroidered in a subtle Navy on the side, and the Memento Mori skull is embroidered in dark charcoal with metallic silver.

Ships with factory flat visor, but you can curve as you wish.

Limited Edition.

name: New Era 5950 Fitted Cap - All Black - New Logo
description:
Here is a new version of the All Black fitted 5950 Cap by New Era.

Revised logo that features "G" and also has no outline embroidery for a cleaner look.  I guess I could call this Stealth 2.0.

All black, with the exception of a dark charcoal outline on the Memento Mori skull on the back.

Ships with factory flat visor, but you can curve as you wish.

name: New Era 5950 Fitted Cap - White with Silver
description:
Just in time for summer!  An all white limited edition New Era Fitted 5950 cap.

This cap features a metallic silver Square & Compass in raised embroidery with the "G".  Also features the New Era Flag on the side in metallic silver, as well as the Memento Mori skull on the back in metallic silver.  And just for a slight contrast, the undervisor is light grey.

Ships with factory flat visor, but you can curve as you wish.

Limited to 18 caps.

description:

1 1/4" round campaign button.  

2BE1 ASK1 in bold classic font bordered by red stripes

Small discrete Square and Compass.

Perfect for your jacket, shirt, or cap.

description:
This is New Era's original fitted cap. The 59FIFTY fitted requires 22 steps to make it perfect. name: "Deus Videt" All Seeing Button
description:
Here we have the all seeing eye inside a triangle formed by hands.

With the latin phrase " Deus Videt".  I wear this as a reminder that "God is watching". 

Standard campaign button that is 1-1/4".  

Available in white or metal.

name: "Time Flies" Button
description:
Here we have a button with the latin phrases "Tempus Fugit" and "Memento Mori".  I like to wear this button to remind that we are only on this earth for a short time, and that I better do the best that I can with what little time I have.

Time Flies.

Standard campaign button that is 1-1/4".  Available in white or metal.

name: Be A Good Husband!
description:
In preparation for my upcoming wedding anniversary, I made a button in honour of my wife.  Now one-offs always cost more then getting them made in batches, so I had a small batch made and figured I'd offer them here.  Now I know these are not Masonic, but hey, aren't we all trying to be better men?  And what better way to show your wife you love her.  Especially the next time you are stepping out to Lodge.

Button is campaign style and is 1 1/4" in diameter.

name: New Era 5950 Fitted Cap - All White
description:
Summer is coming so here we have an All White fitted New Era cap.

Features all white Square & Compass in raised embroidery with "G" on the front, as well as the Memento Mori skull in off white on the back.

Ships with factory flat visor, but you can curve as you wish.

This is a limited edition of only 18 caps.

description:

Will feature a black raised 3D embroidered Square & Compass with graphite outline.  The Memento Mori skull n bones on the back in graphite/grey.  This version features a "vintage" kelly green under visor.

Same high quality as the 59Fifty fitted, but with an adjustable snap-back.

Ships with factory flat visor, but you can curve as you wish.

Remember if you are an active Mason to contact me for a discount code.
